# dominos Provider



## Example Usage

```terraform
provider "dominos" {
  first_name    = "My"
  last_name     = "Name"
  email_address = "my@name.com"
  phone_number  = "15555555555"

  credit_card {
    number = 123456789101112
    cvv    = 1314
    date   = "15/16"
    zip    = 18192
  }
}
```
